{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeBadgeComponentTokensProvider"]]},"sections":[],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeBadgeComponentTokensProvider\/TokensProvider-Implementations","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"kind":"article","topicSections":[{"title":"Instance Methods","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeBadgeComponentTokensProvider\/checkInstances(count:for:)"],"generated":true,"anchor":"Instance-Methods"}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemebadgecomponenttokensprovider\/tokensprovider-implementations"]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"metadata":{"title":"TokensProvider Implementations","modules":[{"name":"Theme Orange"}],"roleHeading":"API Collection","role":"collectionGroup"},"references":{"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeThemeBadgeComponentTokensProvider":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeBadgeComponentTokensProvider","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OrangeThemeBadgeComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemebadgecomponenttokensprovider","title":"OrangeThemeBadgeComponentTokensProvider","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OrangeThemeBadgeComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A class which wraps all "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"component  tokens of badge"}]},{"type":"text","text":" for "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"badge","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" objects like "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSBadge"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This provider should be integrated as a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllBadgeComponentTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation inside "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation to use."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Custom themes can use subclass of "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeBadgeComponentTokensProvider","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" and apply the provider they need."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It implements also the protocol "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"BadgeComponentTokens"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to expose the component tokens for "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"badge","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" through any "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Badge","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" components tokens are defined with semantic tokens of dimensions ("},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllDimensionSemanticTokensProviders"},{"type":"text","text":"),"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and spaces (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":")."}]},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeThemeBadgeComponentTokensProvider/checkInstances(count:for:)":{"title":"checkInstances(count:for:)","fragments":[{"kind":"ke